    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once done, drain and return to the pot to steam dry</p><p>Return the potatoes to a low heat with a knob of <strong>butter</strong> and a splash of <strong>milk</strong></p><p>Season with a grind of <strong>black</strong> <strong>pepper</strong> and mash until smooth</p>",
